  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK144">
<l>eṉaittuṇaiya rāyiṉu meṉṉān tiṉaittuṇaiyun</l>
<l>tērāṉ piṟaṉil pukal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>However great they may be, what's the use? if, thoughtlessly, one enter</l>
<l>even as far as a millet grain into the "house" of another man</l>
<l>(Alternative interpretation not mentioned by commentators:</l>
<l>"However great they may be, what's the use? if they enter unawares</l>
<l>even as far as a millet grain into the "house" of another man)</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
